{"tid":205683,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"水牛遭兩獅狂噬    同伴奮不顧身幫拖嚇退獅子","createTime":"2017-04-18T03:12:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-18T08:24:47.000Z","uid":48093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7f416a3f9de56b5cb9b3bdf62ede302af048d941","tid":205683,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T03:12:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170417/large/1492421524_4bc1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170417%2Flarge%2F1492421524_4bc1.jpg&h=64d177f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n南非克留格爾國家公園一隻年輕離群水牛遭兩隻獅子襲擊，就在牠快要成為獅子點心之際，水牛同伴蜂群而出救牠一命，更將兩隻獅子嚇得落荒而逃。<br />\n<br />\nfacebook組群Calao camp上周二將片段上傳互聯網，可見兩隻飢腸轆轆的獅子在草原上徘徊，一隻年輕水牛離開牛群吃草，發現自己身陷險境時經已太遲，頂著一頭利角的牠先與兩隻獅子對峙，更一度衝向牠們來個下馬威，不過兩隻獅子也不是省油的燈，其中一隻從後將牠撲倒地上，另一隻索性擒在牠身上，兩獅張開血盤大口，水牛不停掙扎卻始終寡不敵眾，被咬到四腳朝天連聲大叫。<br />\n<br />\n由於兩隻獅子仍然年輕，牠們遲遲未發動致命一擊。此時水牛群似是聽到同伴求救聲，一行至少十隻浩浩蕩蕩衝過來，有水牛更用利角一下撞向獅子，令其中一隻獅子馬上知難而退。另一隻初時仍不願放棄口中肥肉，但一群水牛衝到同伴身邊，牠面對來勢洶洶的水牛群，終也知難而退落荒而逃。"},{"pid":"db691728de1ed5acdfbf16274cd15e186aa890b7","tid":205683,"uid":23902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T03:13:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28158eef42cc175a58753d272e29cc2e3d30d367","tid":205683,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T03:14:26.000Z","msg":"好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"019b3cb7cbc6544a152a9bbc6efe8110762a664a","tid":205683,"uid":2305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T03:21:52.000Z","msg":"Video link呢？"},{"pid":"10fc99e3cc7bb378d3425242b04e4253768877d7","tid":205683,"uid":11977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T03:26:29.000Z","msg":"獅子好慘 冇野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n牛牛慘d 比獅子咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbb6fcc0a82f27b079ec40e8c4ba0dc6720f288c","tid":205683,"uid":38172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T03:30:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/458397980869089/videos/1466944426681101/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F458397980869089%2Fvideos%2F1466944426681101%2F&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19p4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=29e5924f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/458397980869089/videos/1466944426681101/</a>"},{"pid":"0134858267531b10eca1ce6da173e8c06b0de8a4","tid":205683,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T03:33:37.000Z","msg":"細個嗰陣老豆成日話D水牛咁蠢，唔識得大人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5be8e9fe067ce54a941b0a0fe628e59d316462a","tid":205683,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T03:39:41.000Z","msg":"右下張相好似講緊：仆街！走先"},{"pid":"d42e0e0bf48efb0ff14a4e0174b9233adb08a889","tid":205683,"uid":2613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T03:41:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>右下張相好似講緊：仆街！走先</blockquote><br />\n開post冇圖嘅下場"},{"pid":"1eef28941c0ae1958ad357f9b98bfcc52acacbb3","tid":205683,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T03:44:07.000Z","msg":"好感動"},{"pid":"bd366f117d989e57de661cd803cb8dbdae888837","tid":205683,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T08:09:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4b70fdaf288e597a7e1c0e39101b7cfd9c5dec6a","tid":205683,"uid":41317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T08:13:25.000Z","msg":"請問可憐水牛定可憐獅子嘅口德分高啲?"},{"pid":"8e5695c6fed3c6fc5042e7718374801f0c40d62b","tid":205683,"uid":8964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-18T08:24:47.000Z","msg":"連牛都識反抗 <br />\n港豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" clas